        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恼恨王允太不仁，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵上马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "屡害平贵所为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫声三姐快开窑门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听门外有人唤，\n想是薛郎回窑前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "开开窑门用目看、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵进窑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "薛郎怎得荣耀还？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎，回来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你哪里来得这身荣耀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因降了红鬃烈马，唐王见喜，将俺封为后军督府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢！如此说来，你作了官了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "作了官了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我谢天谢地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！慢谢天地，其中有变。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此话从何说起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐！只因西凉下国，打来连环战表，要夺我主江山社稷；可恨你父上殿奏本，\n保苏龙魏虎以为正副元帅，将俺后军督府改为马前先行。为此全身披挂回至\n寒窑，辞别三姐，我就要启程了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就要启程了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏晕倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言吓得我魂魄飘洒，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛平贵 （同三叫头） （薛郎）（三姐）！（我夫）我妻）！（夫哇）（妻呀）！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由人一阵阵泪流如麻。\n父好比汉萧何私造律法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父好比秦赵高指鹿为马、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么秦赵高指鹿为马，\n讲什么汉萧何私造律法。\n害得我夫妻们各奔天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "你的父与平贵冤仇结下、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手指着相府高声"
        },
        {
          "character": "你的父与平贵冤仇结下、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫骂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "你的父与平贵冤仇结下、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狠心的爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "你的父与平贵冤仇结下、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你去后为妻我怎度生涯？"
        },
        {
          "character": "爹爹作事理太差、好端端鸳鸯遭棒打、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "爹爹作事理太差、好端端鸳鸯遭棒打、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三姐不必泪双流，\n平贵言来听从头：\n你在寒窑苦度春秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "爹爹作事理太差、好端端鸳鸯遭棒打、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "爹爹作事理太差、好端端鸳鸯遭棒打、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "难度光阴你将我丢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "干柴十担米八斗、守得住来将我守、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "薛郎说话没来由，\n为妻言来听从头：\n留在寒窑度春秋。\n饿死寒窑也不回头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "干柴十担米八斗、夫妻恩深情义厚、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "干柴十担米八斗、夫妻恩深情义厚、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三姐情义世少有，\n倒叫平贵脸含羞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平贵听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵出窑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅初点大卯，不可违误卯期，速到校场听点！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军不下马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各自奔前程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军下，薛平贵进窑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎，外面何人到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐！中军到此传令：元帅初点大卯，不可违误卯期。一卯不到一捆四十；二\n卯不到两捆八十；三卯不到人头落地。军务紧急，我就要启程了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎你……这就要走么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军务要紧哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有什么言语，嘱咐为妻几句吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！此时我心如刀割，纵有满腹的言语，一时也讲不出来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎啊！你今此去，不定三年五载，才得回来，撇下为妻何以度日呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐！方才言得明白，寒窑现有干柴十担，老米八斗，你在寒窑苦度贫寒……"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若是不够呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若是不够，你……回转相府去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎啊！你可记得我在相府与我爹爹三击掌，纵然饿在死寒窑，也是不回去的\n了哇……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好哇！三姐心如铁石，令人可敬。为丈夫此番出征，不定三年五载，才得回来，\n你在这窑前、窑后、窑左、窑右，与人家浆浆洗洗，缝缝连连，耐等为丈夫\n回来，我是一家一家地登门叩谢。话已讲明，我就要启程了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎当真要走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当真要走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然要走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军务紧急呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待为妻送你一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面风大，不送也罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我一定要送。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此有劳了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵出窑门，头碰门上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "碰着了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妨事。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵、王宝钏同出窑，薛平贵牵马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "王宝钏送薛郎心酸难忍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倾刻间夫妻们就要离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但愿得此一去旗开得胜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自有那探马儿来报信音。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一路上必须要保重谨慎，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你在这寒窑内苦度光阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "送薛郎送至在三岔路口，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀，我的夫啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫人难舍又难分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "从空降下无情剑"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "斩断人间夫妻情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "流泪眼观流泪眼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "断肠人送断肠人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宝钏舍不得薛平贵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵难舍妻宝钏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛平贵 （同哭头） 夫妻们只哭得泪如雨降，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏、薛平贵同相望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛平贵 （同哭头） （夫）（妻）呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（号炮三声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又听号炮响连声。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏扯住薛平贵，薛平贵、王宝钏同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "扯住薛郎不放行。\n你要走来将我带！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你苦苦的拉我为何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你去不定三五载，\n你把为妻怎安排？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你回寒窑且忍耐，\n我到军前再作安排。\n（王宝钏扯住薛平贵，薛平贵推王宝钏，王宝钏倒地。薛平贵拉马欲行，见状复回，搀起王宝钏。薛平贵上\n马，王宝钏追，扯缰绳，薛平贵拔剑斩断缰绳，王宝钏趺倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "此时间顾不得夫妻恩爱、薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姐，你要保重了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下。王宝钏立起，望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛郎，我夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！我的夫啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "剑斩缰绳人不在，\n夫妻生生两分开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏回窑，关门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "苦守寒窑望夫来。"
        },
